<plot>A girl films her boyfriend and asks questions about the first day they met. The narrative flashes back and forth from this 'present day' video log, to the nervous, and semi-awkward going-ons of a boy getting ready for girls to come over to his house. From embarrassing and hysterical camp stories, to confrontational moments between drifting friends, you'll feel like you are back home during your first winter-break from college.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?383879</url></doc>
